Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:58.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be2}ワガママMirror heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:03.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be2}逆さまに純情揺れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:07.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be2}君からは裏腹に映るの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be2}それでもMirror heart
