Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:53.06,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Please don't please wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:56.73,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我明明想大聲喊出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:58.82,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}任性的Mirror heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:03.03,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒映著的純情在搖擺不定
