Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.09,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:20.47,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快注意到啊
